"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"main2-23-002","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"心","body":"這首歌曲，是凝聚大～家的開心！所做成的，\n非常棒的歌曲喔！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"main2-23-003","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"香澄","body":"那麼，要上囉！\n『TWiNKLE CiRCLE』！！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"kime01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"main2-23-004","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"蘭","body":"（用音樂牽繫起來的天空。不管天空有多麼遼闊，只要有音樂，\n我們就會是「一如往常」的我們。）","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"main2-23-005","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"彩","body":"（音樂，是閃閃發亮的夢想！舞台的燈光撒在身上，\n讓我們變得更加更加耀眼！希望總有一天，\n能將這個夢想傳達到某個人的心裡。）","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"main2-23-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"心","body":"音樂是讓大～～家露出笑容得魔法咒語！\n只要有音樂，大家就不孤單！\n有我！跟大家一起喔！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"jaan01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"main2-23-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":21}],"windowDisplayName":"友希那","body":"（音樂是光。有時，看見那耀眼的光芒會令人頭暈目眩。\n但是，越是眩目不已，影子的輪廓就會變得更是鮮明。\n我們的榮耀……也會化作濃墨重彩又鮮明的輪廓。）","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":21,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":21,"voiceId":"main2-23-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"香澄","body":"（音樂是我。是可以帶上各種心情傳達出去的我！\n只要有我，還有大家在，就能繼續產生新的歌曲！\n最喜歡了！）","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"main2-23-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"一同","body":"（所以……）","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":0,"voiceId":"main2-23-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"一同","body":"音樂，最開心了！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":0,"voiceId":"main2-23-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"麻里奈","body":"各位，辛苦你們了～～～！！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"main2-23-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"麻里奈","body":"每一個樂團都真的表現超棒的喔！！\n還有，最後的共同樂團！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"main2-23-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"麻里奈","body":"大家的訊息都有傳達出去了，我……\n我都鼻酸了啦。不行，現在感覺也快哭了……！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"main2-23-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":8}],"windowDisplayName":"緋瑪麗","body":"我也快哭了啦～！！嗚嗚，有辦成功真的太好了……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":8,"motionName":"cry01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":8,"voiceId":"main2-23-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"日菜","body":"啊哈哈！小彩跟小緋瑪麗都在哭耶～！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"main2-23-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"紗夜","body":"日菜，你不要這樣捉弄其他人！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"angry01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"main2-23-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"薰","body":"哎呀……但真的是一場非常美好的Live喔。\n來參加的觀眾們，應該都會再一次\n對於樂團抱持興趣了吧。","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"main2-23-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"有咲","body":"不過，這算是很有我們的風格，也是最好的做法了吧？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"main2-23-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"香澄","body":"嗚嗚……！有咲～！！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"cry01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"main2-23-020","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"有咲","body":"煩死了～！你不要抱過來啦！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"shame01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"main2-23-021","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":322}],"windowDisplayName":"真白","body":"那……那個！！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":322,"motionName":"angry01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":322,"voiceId":"main2-23-022","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"香澄","body":"小真白！！你有來看啊？\n謝謝你！！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"main2-23-023","volume":